title: no faces found for ***.png, copying without faces
body:
when i run convert command，Too many “no faces found for ***.png, copying without faces” in the log
but i didn't delete anything in data_dst/aligned, and Face actually exists in the picture，

i guess maybe some package of python about face detection is too old，
